column5: Really? No one found this video funny?
No, not really, shows the mentality of the people, you can really cause a lot of grief when panic turns the wrong way and people start stampeding..
Typical Russian nonsense. Putting on a show for the camera. I'm surprised Harper and the boys have not stooped to this on the Hill.
So it's acceptable to start throwing eggs and beating each other in the face because you disagree with them? oh ok
What I want to know is this - who the hell takes smoke bombs to a parliament meeting? Oh, Ukrainian politicians obviously.
